text: Daniele Bracciali and David Marrero were the defending champions but decided not to participate. Johan Brunström and Frederik Nielsen won this tournament, defeating Jamie Delgado and Jonathan Marray 5–7, 6–2, [10–7] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==External links== * Main Draw Internazionali di Monza e Brianza - Doubles Category:Internazionali di Monza E Brianza
